Homemade Ice Cream
source|
url|
aliases|
tags|
activeTime|
totalTime|1 hour
yield|
description|

# ingredients
1/2|cup|granulated sugar
1|tsp|vanilla extract
1|pint|half'n'half

# instructions
Mix ingredients in small can. (EX: small coffee can)
In large coffee can, Place small coffee can w/ lid on. And cover with ice cubes and 1/4 c. rock salt.
Shake and roll cans for at least 1/2 hour.
